{"tid":1597922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彩虹去西貢1A小巴 有個女仔無啦啦比藍絲廢老鬧","createTime":"2019-09-27T07:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T08:01:57.000Z","uid":308885,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4b51937f5aabb4894cdba201476ac8909a74553d","tid":1597922,"uid":308885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"頭先喺彩虹坐小巴入西貢，有個女仔同一個女人上車，應該兩母女嚟。<br />\n個廢老坐單人位第二個。個阿媽行過佢都冇嘢，個女仔一行佢就用隻腳攔住個女仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個女仔啱啱上車乜都冇做，就因為著深藍色衫著到全身黑色就比個廢老攔住咗。<br />\n個阿媽見到咁就講咗聲唔該叫個廢老讓比佢過，然後個廢老就開鬧，屌鳩個女仔敗亂香港，個女仔睇落都唔係好大唔係好識反應。<br />\n好彩另外有個後生仔同司機幫口，個司機就叫個女仔坐佢後面個位，個廢老就冇哂聲。<br />\n我坐後面影唔到廢老正面，但廢老喺南圍落車，有冇可能靠呢兩張相起佢底 搞搞佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇理由由得佢比人搞唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我隱隱約約見到個女仔手上攞住本自由之夏，應該係同路人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n絲打岀街真係要小心，岀面好多藍屍廢老都好痴線，癲起上嚟唔知會做啲咩，各位巴打見到麻煩幫一幫手保護。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868efd668b2adc2001e87f0a19bbc3b0cac8e346","tid":1597922,"uid":77788,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db487e4e5295299d9295b5028edee368d1a78629","tid":1597922,"uid":106988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:27:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bd0fe30953890b20ea8352a1368411ea5b69c86f","tid":1597922,"uid":122134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"廢老你都淆?<br />\n當面屌柒佢啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cf08c156caf160982e9ce5ab46ea2ccf334564","tid":1597922,"uid":190895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:28:27.000Z","msg":"行過去屌佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e22d1ac8f6d275ef708f004722127950d977a0","tid":1597922,"uid":164590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:29:39.000Z","msg":"落車時屌佢老母"},{"pid":"0f4759d2f18de4a54c0ec38239553cdefb011edb","tid":1597922,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:30:36.000Z","msg":"兜口兜面影啦 驚閪"},{"pid":"892c10bf3152c08ea83b814880619fe95c030eb5","tid":1597922,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:31:01.000Z","msg":"一野推佢落車啦 仲同佢講咁多"},{"pid":"b15fcb8c8f6692dfb6e1dc61a3d2c016c12d2bc7","tid":1597922,"uid":10503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"正面都唔敢影<br />\n唔當面屌7佢<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"91615e577bce9a5016dc7e6db760da54495ec3b2","tid":1597922,"uid":111644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:31:30.000Z","msg":"我坐你後面"},{"pid":"9095bd266018f258b2563a2fb292a9219245c758","tid":1597922,"uid":8589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:31:53.000Z","msg":"屌 上黎講有閪用咩 今時今日廢老都唔敢當面屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5e291097958abff68547fe52babbd194c9d18e","tid":1597922,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"屌柒佢啦，落車一腳推落去叫佢落快啲唔好阻撚住"},{"pid":"85336f739d6fbed68386763deee3be5a024c34f5","tid":1597922,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"西貢就神獸佢啦"},{"pid":"67e283f388db04e12ef90ae1b2777a603d2cf341","tid":1597922,"uid":274435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"咁你又唔撚幫手"},{"pid":"81883e2bb5e1027115b44418e